---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="TekMoral — AI‑Ready Websites & Apps that Grow Your Business"
  description="We build high-converting websites, custom web applications, and AI solutions for SMEs, schools, and startups in Lagos, Nigeria. Fast deployment, optimized performance, built to scale."
  ogImage="https://www.tekmoral.com/og-home.png"
>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-900/30 via-sky-600/10 to-slate-950"></div>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sky-300/90 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mx-auto">
          <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-sky-400"></span>
          TekMoral
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-semibold leading-tight">
          Empowering Businesses and Transforming Lives Through Technology
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-300/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          We design high-converting websites, custom web applications, and AI solutions for SMEs,
          schools, and startups. Deployed fast, optimized for performance, and built to scale.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3 pt-2">
          <a href="/book-a-call" class="px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-400 text-slate-900 font-semibold">
            Send a Message
          </a>
          <a href="#services" class="px-5 py-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-800/80 border border-slate-600 text-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-700 hover:border-slate-400 shadow-sm">
            Explore Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800/60 rounded-2xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-6">Why Your Business Needs Modern Digital Solutions</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-300/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed">
        In today's competitive landscape, businesses that don't adapt to digital transformation risk being left behind. 
        Your customers expect seamless online experiences, instant responses, and intelligent solutions.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-16 divide-y divide-slate-800/60 md:divide-y-0">
      <div class="text-center py-4 md:py-0">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L4.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-50">Outdated Systems Hold You Back</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300/80">Manual processes, paper records, and legacy systems slow down operations and create bottlenecks that frustrate customers and staff.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center py-4 md:py-0">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-50">Competition Moves Fast</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300/80">Competitors with modern websites, automated workflows, and AI-powered insights are capturing market share while you're still catching up.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center py-4 md:py-0">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-sky-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sky-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-50">Growth Requires Scale</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300/80">As your business grows, you need systems that can handle increased demand without proportionally increasing costs or complexity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900/50 to-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-700/50">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-slate-50">The Solution: Strategic Digital Transformation</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-300/90 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We don't just build websites and apps—we create digital ecosystems that solve real business problems. 
          From automating repetitive tasks to providing AI-powered insights, our solutions help you work smarter, 
          serve customers better, and scale efficiently.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-stretch gap-3 text-sm text-slate-400 text-left divide-y divide-slate-700/60 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:justify-center sm:items-center sm:gap-4 sm:divide-y-0">
          <span class="flex items-start gap-2 py-2 sm:py-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 flex-none" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Faster Operations
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-start gap-2 py-2 sm:py-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 flex-none" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Better Customer Experience
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-start gap-2 py-2 sm:py-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 flex-none" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Data-Driven Decisions
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-start gap-2 py-2 sm:py-0">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400 flex-none" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            Scalable Growth
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 p-6 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-slate-700 hover:ring-sky-400/70 transition duration-300 ease-out transform-gpu hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.01] motion-reduce:transform-none after:absolute after:inset-0 after:opacity-0 group-hover:after:opacity-100 after:transition after:bg-[radial-gradient(400px_120px_at_20%_-20%,rgba(56,189,248,0.20),transparent_60%)]">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-50">Business Websites & Branding</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300/80">Professional sites, landing pages, and brand systems optimized for conversion. Optional AI chatbots to engage visitors.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 p-6 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-slate-700 hover:ring-sky-400/70 transition duration-300 ease-out transform-gpu hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.01] motion-reduce:transform-none after:absolute after:inset-0 after:opacity-0 group-hover:after:opacity-100 after:transition after:bg-[radial-gradient(400px_120px_at_20%_-20%,rgba(56,189,248,0.20),transparent_60%)]">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-50">Custom Web Applications</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300/80">Management systems, portals with authentication, dashboards, and AI automation for reporting and insights.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 p-6 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-slate-700 hover:ring-sky-400/70 transition duration-300 ease-out transform-gpu hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.01] motion-reduce:transform-none after:absolute after:inset-0 after:opacity-0 group-hover:after:opacity-100 after:transition after:bg-[radial-gradient(400px_120px_at_20%_-20%,rgba(56,189,248,0.20),transparent_60%)]">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-50">Tech Consulting & Training</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300/80">Digital transformation guidance, web/cloud training, and introductory AI/ML programs for teams and schools.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 p-6 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-slate-700 hover:ring-sky-400/70 transition duration-300 ease-out transform-gpu hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.01] motion-reduce:transform-none after:absolute after:inset-0 after:opacity-0 group-hover:after:opacity-100 after:transition after:bg-[radial-gradient(400px_120px_at_20%_-20%,rgba(56,189,248,0.20),transparent_60%)]">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-50">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300/80">Predictive analytics, chat/assistants, and models tailored to business goals, including trading insights.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 p-6 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.45)] ring-1 ring-slate-700 hover:ring-sky-400/70 transition duration-300 ease-out transform-gpu hover:-translate-y-1 hover:scale-[1.01] motion-reduce:transform-none after:absolute after:inset-0 after:opacity-0 group-hover:after:opacity-100 after:transition after:bg-[radial-gradient(400px_120px_at_20%_-20%,rgba(56,189,248,0.20),transparent_60%)] sm:col-span-2">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-50">School Solutions</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-300/80">Smart school portals with digital records & analytics, plus affordable static quiz/practice platforms optimized for mobile.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>